channel.title: Editing Admin Character
channel.description: I am using Cheezscape and everytime I edit the admin character text file under characters and login it reverts back to either a new character or old data... how can I overwrite this?

item.title: Editing Admin Character
item.dc:creator: @_Vengeance _Vengeance
item.description:

[quote=“joshlolzorzfuckinpwnzz, post:2, topic:185073”]The person who edited it before you got it, made it so that it is only able to make them mod/admin.

The player which was already on there, which is probably “Admin” that player wil be admin, and that sdtatus is only one you can change, sorry to break this to you

i suggest you find another source, satan’s isle is a VERY good source. alot on it but soo EASY to edit!

Have fun :)[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 29, 2008, 01:25:54 AM[/size][hr]Oh and…

Cheezscape player saving/loading i know for a fact is absolute shit. Fix the loading method to load from the directory you want.
